development of bilateral economic, trade and financial
cooperation, and that these problems can be solved through
constant consultations.
</P>
<P>
Siazon agreed with Rong, saying that bilateral relations have
developed satisfactorily during the past year, and he hopes
that future cooperation will continue.  
