<HEADLINE> International Economic Conference on Investment in </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, June 7 (Xinhua) -- An international economic conference
on investment in Egypt will convene in London on June 27, local
press reports said today.
</P>
<P>
The conference will be attended by representatives from around
150 international companies, said the reports.
</P>
<P>
The U.S Chamber of Commerce in Egypt is organizing the
conference to discuss elements of continuous attraction for
investors in Egypt in addition to details of economic reform, free
market policies, investment opportunities in the country.
</P>
<P>
The conference is also to review facilities offered by the
government for investors and the best area of investment in Egypt,
according to the reports.
</P>
