Surabaya, East Java, Pontianak, Banjarnasin and Bukittinggi.
</P>
<P>
More than 500 participants had enrolled for the tournament.
</P>
<P>
The 1996 Worldwide Bridge Contest is coordinated in Paris, to
which results of tournaments in different parts of the world would
be reported. 
