Zengcheng, Conghua and Huadu cities will also rise to eight digits
simultaneously.
</P>
<P>
People calling from foreign countries or from Hong Kong, Macao
and Taiwan regions must, after dialing China's country code of
"86" and the area code "20", add 8 before the original first
numbers 2 and 7, or add 1 if the original first number was 8.
