China's Special Economic Zones, thanks to the computer network of
the hotel where he lived.
</P>
<P>
On the same day police in Guangzhou, capital city of the
province, caught Liang Fuhua and Liang Guanhui, who murdered two
people and robbed 45,000 yuan in Changsha city, central China's
Hunan Province. 
