plans in both the new area of Thilawa Port and the area of Yangon
Port, Myanmar's principal trading center and the premier port,
which handles virtually all imports and over 90 percent of
exports.
</P>
<P>
At present, the Yangon Port handles only about 7 million tons
of cargo annually.
</P>
<P>
