<HEADLINE> Chile Draws Argentina in Libertadores Semifinal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTIAGO, June 6 (Xinhua) -- Universidad de Chile and River
Plate of Argentina played a 2-2 draw in the semifinal of the Copa
Libertadores soccer tournament here on Wednesday night.
</P>
<P>
Uruguayan Enzo Francescoli netted the first for River Plate in
the 22nd minute with a 30-meter lob.
</P>
<P>
