a pass off Argentine Leonardo Rodriguez.
</P>
<P>
In the 76th minute, River Plate who resorted to a defensive
game, scored their late equaliser through Juan Pablo Sorin.
</P>
<P>
After the match ended in a 2-2 draw, fans of both sides clashed
against each other with rocks and bottles outside the stadium, and
some 20 people were arrested in the incidents. 
